[Marcel Pilet-Golaz](/Marcel_Pilet-Golaz), [Winston Churchill](/Winston_Churchill), [Grigore Gafencu](/Grigore_Gafencu), [Édouard Daladier](/%C3%89douard_Daladier), [Albert-Édouard Janssen](/Albert-Edouard_Janssen), [Antony Eden](/Anthony_Eden), [Juraj Krnjevic](/Juraj_Krnjevic), [Knut Kristensen](/Knud_Kristensen), [Indalecio Prieto](/Indalecio_Prieto), [Hjalmar J. Procopé](/Hjalmar_Procop%C3%A9), [Paul Ramadier](/Paul_Ramadier), [Paul Reynaud](/Paul_Reynaud), [Tadeusz Romer](/Tadeusz_Romer), [Paul van Zeeland](/Paul_van_Zeeland), Jacques Augarde, [Gustav Heinemann](/Gustav_Heinemann), [Johannes Hoffmann](/Johannes_Hoffmann_(CVP)), [François Mitterrand](/Fran%C3%A7ois_Mitterrand), [Konrad Adenauer](/Konrad_Adenauer), [Duncan Sandys](/Duncan_Sandys), [Józef Retinger](/J%C3%B3zef_Retinger), Léon Chevalme, Alphonse Colle, Maurice Schumann, Auguste Cool, Henri Lambotte, Henri Davezac, Ivo Duchacek, [Carl Romme](/Carl_Romme), Gaston Tessier, [Živko Topalović](/%C5%BDivko_Topalovi%C4%87), Édouard Bonnefous, Georges Chevrot, [Paolo Giobbe](/Paolo_Giobbe); André François-Poncet, André Lefèvre, marquis d'Ormesson, [Nicolò Carandini](/Nicol%C3%B2_Carandini), Étienne Gilson, Charles Morgan, Bertrand Russell, [Salvador de Madariaga](/Salvador_de_Madariaga); Raymond Rifflet, [William Rappard](/William_Rappard), [Walter Hallstein](/Walter_Hallstein), René Capitant, Léon Julliot, [Lord Moran](/Charles_Wilson,_1st_Baron_Moran), Michel Polonowski, [Émile Borel](/%C3%89mile_Borel), [Gilbert Murray](/Gilbert_Murray), [Peter Fleming](/Peter_Fleming_(writer)), Henry de Ségogne, [Jacques Rueff](/Jacques_Rueff), Maurice Allais, [Jan Tinbergen](/Jan_Tinbergen), Harold Butler, Louis Salleron, Jacques Lacour-Gayet, Pierre Hély d’Oissel, Pieter Otten, [Adrian Boult](/Adrian_Boult), [Paul Landowski](/Paul_Landowski), Raymond Aron, René Courtin, [Walter Layton](/Walter_Layton,_1st_Baron_Layton), [Jan Piłsudski](/Jan_Pi%C5%82sudski), Raymond Silva, [Gilberte Brossolette](/Gilberte_Brossolette),